subject: Re: New file uploaded to Read_Alphabet
msgSnippet: Please count me among those who are quite interested in the additions/modifications to Quikscript that you propose. It seems to me that any system of writing,
messageBody: Please count me among those who are quite interested in the additions/modifications to Quikscript that you propose. It seems to me that any system of writing, whether primarily phonetic or alphabetic, can evolve over time to incorporate substantial modifications to its original design while preserving the system's essence; thoughtful proposals from Quikscript writers like you, along with the pro-and-con deliberations that they stimulate, provide the mechanism of that evolution.
